{"tid":1786710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 - 支援手足channel","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T13:52:37.000Z","uid":11013,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"893fbc83f97bf1603f091e0ed829db674c0e0359","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">（前文）點解有支足channel?</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784898</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">gofundme</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/4ubp58-stand-with-hong-kong?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cf+share-flow-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2F4ubp58-stand-with-hong-kong%3Futm_source%3Dcustomer%26utm_medium%3Dcopy_link%26utm_campaign%3Dp_cf%2Bshare-flow-1&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=cf3d6e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/4ubp58-stand-with-hong-kong?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cf+share-flow-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">tg 支足channel （請入）</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=c2de3296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a><br />\n<br />\n支足channel目的： 希望幫助到 有需要既學生、小朋友、被捕既手足。手足有需要便出聲，唔好怕醜。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足 有力出力 有錢出錢。抗爭得以持續落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足學生小朋友篇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n格式如下：<br />\n1.  想要甚麼援助？（金額多少？八達通？醫療費？飯券？）<br />\n2. 講下而家既困難/處境/生活<br />\n3. 學生證/被捕文件 連手寫連登or tg username (遮個人資料和樣）<br />\n4. 年齡<br />\n5.男or女？ <br />\n<br />\n回覆需時請見諒，一般24小時內回覆。如過24小時未有請重send過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdmin fact check後會開case,搵家長幫手。 完成後會close file<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>所有家長捐贈金額和小朋友所需的金額和物資會紀錄低，定時紀錄在google，公開給大家。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前俾手足既上少少物資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjrZi7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjrZi7e.png&h=27482095&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0P0N0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0P0N0A.png&h=fa1cd73a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axC2gTW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxC2gTW.png&h=ad9b1f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"918c758f670a5065316098b28490a610fa78dec8","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a030fb15f464edf106fa9b69c6e327dc912fb0cd","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"1218f578f72285e6a5b277b2605e3ff3b8cf9010","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2c0b3863e7b56a022d41b280272c5f78bc9ee526","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5aa631d3a281616e03039971af80405f75030c27","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f087c652ef4fab4189d84f2b2d6860500e92e7c9","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4725c10e68445e8ec50cec4ce949744626e1976","tid":1786710,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:49:31.00